overview: Pilkades (village head election) will still be held in a village when the virus pandemic hits. Sunarta is a village head who will nominate again using other means of campaigning other than using MMT. At the same time, mass back pain also occurred in the village, making Bahar a mosque takmir who felt restless because his mosque was always quiet. The unused mosque car also took part in the Sunarta campaign at the Village Health Center.
title: Preeetty Vacant
